 Construction of a PackageUrl is done with a Builder via builder():
PackageUrl purl = PackageUrl.builder() .type(&#34;maven&#34;) .namespace(&#34;junit&#34;) .name(&#34;junit&#34;) .version(&#34;4.12&#34;) .build(); Mutation Mutation is also handled by a builder by converting an existing PackageUrl into a Builder:
PackageUrl purl = PackageUrl.parse(&#34;pkg:maven/junit/junit@4.12&#34;); PackageUrl purlNoVersion = purl.asBuilder().version(null).build();
